{"tid":1777012,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"渴望孤獨 為何我 這刻會想 重頭覓對象","createTime":"2019-12-10T02:27:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T02:30:45.000Z","uid":317915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e49fa7ace091cebf5a9bf1bb3c4dfa2c31189e78","tid":1777012,"uid":317915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T02:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b78418fd875607a8828a791b4e446615332d316","tid":1777012,"uid":12909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e49fa7ace091cebf5a9bf1bb3c4dfa2c31189e78","tid":1777012,"uid":317915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T02:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T02:40:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0032b2c716c19241352a224cdc7c1d3b4958c837","tid":1777012,"uid":213163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T02:44:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hy3vV3M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHy3vV3M.jpg&h=7e318a13&s={SIZE}\" />唔好意思借個位嚟<br />\n好重要今晚就係啦！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n*已獲不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n~~~~~~~<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【國際人權日．正日集會】</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1948年12月10日，聯合國公佈《世界人權宣言》，確立生而為人的基本權利。走過71年，世界人權仍然是未竟之路。在香港及世界各地，人民仍要為爭取基本的自由及權利奮鬥，甚至有所付出及犧牲。<br />\n<br />\n12月10日晚，我們一起站出來，為香港人加油，也為全球為人權奮鬥的人打氣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">日期：12月10日<br />\n時間：18:30-22:00<br />\n地點：金鐘連儂牆下<br />\n</span><br />\n內容：<br />\n悼念及回顧<br />\n嘉賓講話<br />\n短片欣賞及分享<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LCPK0vx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLCPK0vx.jpg&h=63585984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n推呀屌你再過7個鐘就係啦 唔好再屌鬼啦行動post呢文宣post呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係完咗人權日遊行就end game㗎<br />\n我地仲有訴求㗎！！！<br />\n聽日要見到連儂牆有十萬人呀！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n12月10號 6點半政總見！！"},{"pid":"2ea6bfddbeb50e3feedf3bcd0cc833b5c77e4d50","tid":1777012,"uid":317915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b78418fd875607a8828a791b4e446615332d316","tid":1777012,"uid":12909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e49fa7ace091cebf5a9bf1bb3c4dfa2c31189e78","tid":1777012,"uid":317915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T02:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T02:40:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T04:08:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b48b2f9305c2ba0d8a920fec4aee401b492b03a","tid":1777012,"uid":12909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ea6bfddbeb50e3feedf3bcd0cc833b5c77e4d50","tid":1777012,"uid":317915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b78418fd875607a8828a791b4e446615332d316","tid":1777012,"uid":12909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e49fa7ace091cebf5a9bf1bb3c4dfa2c31189e78","tid":1777012,"uid":317915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T02:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T02:40:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019